## Notes
- Analysis-only; no flight-code or chirp-feature changes.
- `actuator_outputs_N` values are not numerically identical across SITL vs flight (sim PWM-µs vs
  UAVCAN servo units); the comparison is by function and normalized signal.
- This flight log's chirp predates/avoids `CA_CHIRP`, so the comparison validates the output *path/shape*,
  not an identical command; for an apples-to-apples chirp, run the `CA_CHIRP` SITL runner and compare
  against a future flight that uses `CA_CHIRP`.
